Credits for Third-Party Components:

This project uses 'terminal.css' by Jonas D., licensed under the MIT License. The file 'hugo-terminal.css/assets/css/terminal.css-dark.css' is based on the 'terminal.css' theme's dark version. THis file converts it to the dark theme. As for the actual theme it is used through a CDN in 'hugo-terminal.css/layouts/partials/head.html'.

